      <title>摩根大通称香港股市上涨可能受空头回补推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hong-kong-stock-rally-likely-driven-by-short-covering-jpm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，中国央行出台一系列广泛的货币刺激措施后，空头回补可能是推动香港股市周二大幅上涨的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hong-kong-stock-rally-likely-driven-by-short-covering-jpm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
